{"tid":366694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗今日唔出黎真係好蠢","createTime":"2017-08-20T08:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T15:57:38.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"433ccbda793eb75e2a45c2da1ed17723fb275339","tid":366694,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"大把人捐款比眾志社民連<br />\n熱狗食水尾起碼幫補到書展損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060a2fcddad6f8d6e4a30be919a3fcefd459b982","tid":366694,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"雙學三子、反新界東北發展案13名爭取公義的社運人士，在港府律政司窮追猛打下成為階下囚。多個民間組織及政黨今天發起聲援在囚抗爭者遊行，包括多名主要成員因涉不同議題社會運動被囚的社民連及香港眾志，亦有民間人權陣線、新界東北發展關注組等組織。不少遊行人士發聲之餘，出力兼出錢，踴躍籌款，現場所見，印有東北支援組、社民連、香港眾志等標誌的捐款箱，內有不少500元大鈔，其他捐款箱也有很多100元紙幣。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，有大會義工指今日4個民間組織及政黨的所有籌款箱，都被善款塞爆。"},{"pid":"6f5510c722b4d5bb88e3e91a1cafa5913d10f4b1","tid":366694,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1e5291e2cb767816174c5653e5cdcf8ab94d536","tid":366694,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"陳雲要同中共打好關係。好似係"},{"pid":"f7742401827774af57c53e96f9083b2540cf3600","tid":366694,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12013963f28686375ba8e3d2794929e63bbac511","tid":366694,"uid":66536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"熱狗呢兩日仲追擊緊毓民 唔得閒住"},{"pid":"bf10e7cc7d16d7aa21ee0a7cef990936719e00ae","tid":366694,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗呢兩日仲追擊緊毓民 唔得閒住</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9ed89